二、指定教科書及參考資料 Textbooks and Reference(請修課同學遵守智慧財產權，不得非法影印)


●指定教科書 Required TextsHillier, F.S., Hillier, M.S., Introduction to Management Science, A Modeling and Case Studies Approach with Spreadsheet, 2014, International Edition, 5th Edition, McGraw Hill, 華泰。
		●參考書資料暨網路資源 Reference Books and Online Resources


三、教學目標 Objectives


This course is designed for students to discuss business situations, handle prominent non-mathematical issues, use spreadsheets, and learn model formulation and assesment more than model structring. The main element in this course is a modeling and case studies approach with spreadsheets. Students need to join the class participation at least five times and present their group project at the end of the course.　


